short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Roblox JobId Join allows you to join a Roblox server with a specific job ID!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
To join a server, add a `serverJobId=<job-id>` query parameter to the URL. This will automatically launch Roblox much like links with VIP server codes do.

Source Code: https://github.com/DaRealRomz/roblox-jobid-join
